Here are some of the best free AI tools for creators and guides on using AI for content creation:

##Free AI Tools for Creators

Canva: An all-in-one design platform with AI features like Magic Write and Magic Design. It is useful for social media graphics and presentations.
ElevenLabs: Offers AI voice synthesis and voice cloning. This is suitable for narrations and voiceovers.
Descript: This tool edits audio and video by editing the text transcript.

Leonardo AI & Ideogram: These are AI image generators. Leonardo AI provides tokens and style models. Ideogram renders text accurately within images.
Copy.ai: A writing assistant that generates blog posts, ad copy, and social media captions.

Pictory & Lumen5: These tools turn text content into videos with AI-generated voiceovers and stock footage.
Remove.bg: This tool removes backgrounds from images.

ChatGPT/Claude/Gemini: Large Language Models (LLMs) are used for content ideation and drafting.Â 
