Voice Training: High-quality audio samples are needed to train AI on a vocal style. Tools like ElevenLabs and Resemble AI create a synthetic voice model.
Content Ideas: Use AI content idea generators like Noiz.io or iWeaver AI. Input a niche or topic to get ideas for different platforms.Â 

##Content Creation Workflows

Create Images: Use Leonardo AI, Adobe Firefly, or Freepik. These offer styles including photorealistic and anime.
Create Websites & Graphics: Canva is suitable for graphics and simple web pages. Durable AI Website Builder generates a site structure.
Create Logos and Brand Art: Canva can create brand assets using its design tools and AI features. Use AI image generators like Freepik or Recraft AI to generate logo concepts.
Create Viral YouTube Thumbnails: Canva has templates and AI tools to design thumbnails. Pixlr also offers editing features and templates.
Plan, Script, and Create Short-Form Content:
Plan/Script: Use an LLM like ChatGPT or an idea generator like Copy.ai to brainstorm.
Create/Edit: Use CapCut or OpusClip for editing and subtitling.
Create AI B-roll and Videos: Runway and Pika are used for B-roll and video clips. Lumen5 and Pictory turn text into videos using stock footage and voiceovers.
Plan and Create Ads: Copy.ai and Writesonic generate ad copy. Canva is suitable for designing ad visuals.
Plan, Script, and Create YouTube Videos: Notion AI can manage content calendars and organize research. Use Writesonic or Jasper for scripts, then use Descript or Wondershare Filmora for editing.
